  step 61: missing (oracle: "\"It wasn't,\" I reply. \"But I doubt you'd understand.\"\n")
  step 62: missing (oracle: "He simply nods.\n")
  step 63: missing (oracle: "\"Go on with your confession.\"\n")
  step 64: missing (oracle: "That gives me pause. I hadn't thought of it as such. But I suppose he's right. I am about to admit what I did.\n")
  step 65: missing (oracle: "\"There's not much else to say. I took the part from Bombe computing device. You seem to know that already. I had to. He was going to expose me if I didn't.\"\n")
  step 66: missing (oracle: "\"This young man was blackmailing you over your affair?\"\n")
  step 67: missing (oracle: "As Harris speaks I find myself suddenly sharply aware, as if waking from a long sleep. The table, the corrugated walls of the hut, everything seems suddenly more tangible than a moment before.\n")
