  step 43: text differs
    oracle: "He slides his thumb between two fingers.\n"
    brink:  "\"I see.\"\n"
  step 44: text differs
    oracle: "\"Now they own you.\"\n"
    brink:  "There's a long pause, like the delay between feeding a line of cypher into the Bombe and waiting for its valves to warm up enough to begin processing.\n"
  step 45: text differs
    oracle: "\"Harris, I...\"\n"
    brink:  "\"You want to explain that?\"\n"
  step 46: text differs
    oracle: "\"Stop it,\" he interrupts. \"There's no jury here to sway. And there's no time. So why don't you tell me, right now. Where is it?\"\n"
    brink:  "\n"
  step 47: text differs
    oracle: "His eyes bear down like carbonised drill—bits.\n"
    brink:  "I pause a moment, trying to choose my words. To just come out and say it, after a lifetime of hiding... that is a circle I cannot square.\n"
  step 49: text differs
    oracle: "\"All right. I'll tell you what happened.\" And never mind my shame.\n"
    brink:  "I fold my arms, intended firmly to say nothing. But somehow, watching Harris' face, I cannot bring myself to do it. I want to confess. I want to tell him everything I can, to explain myself to him, to earn his forgiveness. The sensation is so strong my will is powerless in the face of it.\n"
  step 50: text differs
    oracle: "\"I can imagine how it starts,\" he replies.\n"
    brink:  "Something is wrong with me, I am sure of it. There is a strange, bitter flavour on my tongue. I taste it as words start to form.\n"
  step 51: text differs
    oracle: "\"There was a young man. I met him in the town. A few months ago now. We got to talking. Not about work. And I used my cover story, but he seemed to know it wasn't true. That got me wondering if he might be one of us.\"\n"
    brink:  "\"I've done things,\" I begin. \"Things I didn't want to do. I tried not to. But in the end, it felt like cutting off my own arm to resist.\"\n"
  step 52: text differs
    oracle: "Harris is not letting me off any more.\n"
    brink:  "\"You mean you've left yourself open,\" Harris answers. \"To pressure. Is that what you're saying?\"\n"
  step 53: text differs
    oracle: "\"You seriously entertained that possibility?\"\n"
    brink:  "\n"
  step 54: text differs
    oracle: "\n"
    brink:  "I shake my head violently, to say no, that's not it, but whatever is wrong with tongue is wrong with neck too. I look across at the table at Harris' face and realise with a start how sympathetic he is. Such a kind, generous man. How can I hold anything back from him?\n"
  step 55: text differs
    oracle: "\"No. Not for more than a moment, of course. Everyone here is marked out by how little we would be willing to say about it.\"\n"
    brink:  "I take another mouthful of the bitter, strange—tasting tea before answering.\n"
  step 56: text differs
    oracle: "\"Only you told this young man more than a little, didn't you?\"\n"
    brink:  "\"That's it,\" I reply. \"There are some things... which a man shouldn't do.\"\n"
  step 57: text differs
    oracle: "I nod. \"He seemed to know all about me. He... he was quite enchanted by my achievements.\"\n"
    brink:  "Harris doesn't stiffen. Doesn't lean away, as though my condition might be infectious. I had thought they trained them in the army to shoot my kind on sight.\n"
  step 58: text differs
    oracle: "The way Harris is staring I expect him to strike me, but he does not. He replies, \"I can see how that must have been attractive to you,\" with such plain—spokeness that I think I must have misheard.\n"
    brink:  "He offers no sympathy either. He nods, once. His understanding of me is a mere turning cog in his calculations, with no meaning to it.\n"
  step 59: text differs
    oracle: "\n"
    brink:  "\"I've seen it before. A young man like you — clever, removed. The kind that doesn't go to parties. Who takes himself too seriously. Who takes things too far.\"\n"
  step 60: text differs
    oracle: "\"It wasn't,\" I reply. \"But I doubt you'd understand.\"\n"
    brink:  "He slides his thumb between two fingers.\n"
  step 61: text differs
    oracle: "He simply nods.\n"
    brink:  "\"Now they own you.\"\n"
  step 62: missing (oracle: "\"Go on with your confession.\"\n")
  step 63: missing (oracle: "That gives me pause. I hadn't thought of it as such. But I suppose he's right. I am about to admit what I did.\n")
  step 64: missing (oracle: "\"There's not much else to say. I took the part from Bombe computing device. You seem to know that already. I had to. He was going to expose me if I didn't.\"\n")
  step 65: missing (oracle: "\"This young man was blackmailing you over your affair?\"\n")
  step 66: missing (oracle: "As Harris speaks I find myself suddenly sharply aware, as if waking from a long sleep. The table, the corrugated walls of the hut, everything seems suddenly more tangible than a moment before.\n")
  step 67: missing (oracle: "Whatever it was they put in my drink is wearing off.\n")

