  step 59: text differs
    oracle: "\"No. Not for more than a moment, of course. Everyone here is marked out by how little we would be willing to say about it.\"\n"
    brink:  "His eyes bear down like carbonised drill—bits.\n"
  step 60: missing (oracle: "\"Only you told this young man more than a little, didn't you?\"\n")
  step 61: missing (oracle: "I nod. \"He seemed to know all about me. He... he was quite enchanted by my achievements.\"\n")
  step 62: missing (oracle: "The way Harris is staring I expect him to strike me, but he does not. He replies, \"I can see how that must have been attractive to you,\" with such plain—spokeness that I think I must have misheard.\n")
  step 63: missing (oracle: "\"It's a lonely life in this place,\" I reply. \"Lonely - and still one never gets a moment to oneself.\"\n")
  step 64: missing (oracle: "\"That's how it is in the Service,\" Harris answers.\n")

