  step 53: text differs
    oracle: "Harris is not letting me off any more.\n"
    brink:  "He offers no sympathy either. He nods, once. His understanding of me is a mere turning cog in his calculations, with no meaning to it.\n"
  step 54: text differs
    oracle: "\"You seriously entertained that possibility?\"\n"
    brink:  "\"I've seen it before. A young man like you — clever, removed. The kind that doesn't go to parties. Who takes himself too seriously. Who takes things too far.\"\n"
  step 55: text differs
    oracle: "\n"
    brink:  "He slides his thumb between two fingers.\n"
  step 56: text differs
    oracle: "\"No. Not for more than a moment, of course. Everyone here is marked out by how little we would be willing to say about it.\"\n"
    brink:  "\"Now they own you.\"\n"
  step 57: text differs
    oracle: "\"Only you told this young man more than a little, didn't you?\"\n"
    brink:  "\n"
  step 58: text differs
    oracle: "I nod. \"He seemed to know all about me. He... he was quite enchanted by my achievements.\"\n"
    brink:  "\"I can still fix this.\"\n"
  step 59: text differs
    oracle: "The way Harris is staring I expect him to strike me, but he does not. He replies, \"I can see how that must have been attractive to you,\" with such plain—spokeness that I think I must have misheard.\n"
    brink:  "Harris shakes his head. \"You'll do nothing. This is beyond you now. You may go to prison or may go to firing squad - or we can change your name and move you somewhere where your indiscretions can't hurt you. But right now, none of that matters. What happens to you doesn't matter. All that matters is where that component is. So why don't you tell me, right now. Where is it?\"\n"
  step 60: text differs
    oracle: "\n"
    brink:  "His eyes bear down like carbonised drill—bits.\n"
  step 61: missing (oracle: "\"It wasn't,\" I reply. \"But I doubt you'd understand.\"\n")
  step 62: missing (oracle: "He simply nods.\n")
  step 63: missing (oracle: "\"Go on with your confession.\"\n")
  step 64: missing (oracle: "That gives me pause. I hadn't thought of it as such. But I suppose he's right. I am about to admit what I did.\n")
  step 65: missing (oracle: "\"There's not much else to say. I took the part from Bombe computing device. You seem to know that already. I had to. He was going to expose me if I didn't.\"\n")
  step 66: missing (oracle: "\"This young man was blackmailing you over your affair?\"\n")
  step 67: missing (oracle: "As Harris speaks I find myself suddenly sharply aware, as if waking from a long sleep. The table, the corrugated walls of the hut, everything seems suddenly more tangible than a moment before.\n")
  step 68: missing (oracle: "Whatever it was they put in my drink is wearing off.\n")

